Marie-Hélène Arnaud https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marie-H%C3%A9l%C3%A8ne_Arnaud 0 Marie-Hélène Françoise Arnaud (24 September 1934 – 6 October 1986) was a French model and actress. Working as a house model for the French fashion house Chanel, she was the "face of Chanel" in the 1950s; she also developed a second career as an actress.
